: "RocketSprocket", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsL9shz0.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/mattvanswol/status/2052827541438706098", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "This seems a bit much...", "last_comment_created": 1778342625704, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 36, "score_up": 340, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": [{"width": 886, "heightRatio": 96, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HH0bhqpWYAcMkC6.png", "height": 852}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 593, "created": 1778267200000, "id": "2052827541438706098", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1580221131985920001/XNlqL_Yx_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Matt Van Swol", "username": "mattvanswol"}, "content": "@harryjsisson Brother...\n\nThis is an actual district in Chicago.", "parentTweet": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 0, "created": 1778264753000, "id": "2052817278333247992", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1766653032983367680/xFjjY0tr_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Harry Sisson", "username": "harryjsisson"}, "content": "If Virginia can\u2019t have their maps, then other blue states need to step up. Eliminate all of the Republican seats like they\u2019re doing to us.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 6093}, "likes": 27467}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsLAzzyX", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 53, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8608515, "raw_content": "Proverbs 25:28 nkjv\n\"Whoever has no rule over his own spirit is like a city broken down, with no walls\"\n\nDo the tough things. Have self control. Make the hard decisions. Do what is best for your family, follow Christ in everything you do. Do not give in to temptation. \nThis scripture reminds me and inspires me to get up everyday and first thank the Lord, spend time in prayer and Bible study. Then to eat healthy, work out, go out and provide for my family and lead them as the Lord wants me to. To not give in to things or behaviors that would harm myself, the ones I love, or be displeasing to our Lord Jesus Christ. \nIts a challenge sometimes to not have that drink or to let anger cause a lack of patience, but the Lord is with me always and hears my prayers when I ask him for the self control and strength I need to be who he wants me to be. \nI don't always succeed because I am imperfect. But our Lord is perfect, he hears our prayers and knows what we need.\nGo to him. Seek him. Ask him to lead you everyday. \nAnd he will bless you.\nGod bless!", "author": "TrevorL", "created": 1778328214901, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Massie_Won", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Proverbs 25:28", "last_comment_created": 1778333327659, "content": "<p>Proverbs 25:28 nkjv\n&quot;Whoever has no rule over his own spirit is like a city broken down, with no walls&quot;</p>\n<p>Do the tough things. Have self control. Make the hard decisions. Do what is best for your family, follow Christ in everything you do. Do not give in to temptation.\nThis scripture reminds me and inspires me to get up everyday and first thank the Lord, spend time in prayer and Bible study. Then to eat healthy, work out, go out and provide for my family and lead them as the Lord wants me to. To not give in to things or behaviors that would harm myself, the ones I love, or be displeasing to our Lord Jesus Christ.\nIts a challenge sometimes to not have that drink or to let anger cause a lack of patience, but the Lord is with me always and hears my prayers when I ask him for the self control and strength I need to be who he wants me to be.\nI don't always succeed because I am imperfect. But our Lord is perfect, he hears our prayers and knows what we need.\nGo to him. Seek him. Ask him to lead you everyday.\nAnd he will bless you.\nGod bless!</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 53, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2053148771555356831", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsLB16dU", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 21, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8608980, "raw_content": "", "author": "KuzoKevin", "created": 1778346255073, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Jakylangelo", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsLB16dU.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/Justinjpearson/status/2053148771555356831", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "\"Oh tay!\" {Buckwheat voice}", "last_comment_created": 1778358024612, "content": "", "sco